National Council Salem Zanoun announced.
</P>
<P>
Zanoun told reporters after the two-day meeting of the 129-
member PCC, the Palestinian policy making body, that the PCC will
meet again before November 15 to decide when to declare an
independent state. (Palestine-Statehood 1st lead-writethru)
