<HEADLINE> Media Forum Established in Zimbabwe  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
According to a draft document made available at a media meeting
in Harare on Sunday, the forum would provide a platform for
information exchange.
</P>
<P>
It would promote increased advocacy role of the media in the
production and dissemination of information.
</P>
<P>
The forum would play a major role in raising awareness on
developmental issues, promote sexual responsibility and social
justice.
</P>
<P>
To this end, a general assembly of media practitioners has been
formed to review activities of the Media Forum and endorse annual
plans of the forum's different organs.
</P>
