production and dissemination of information on population and
development issues, especially HIV/Aids and gender issues.
</P>
<P>
The United Nations Fund for Population Activities was expected
to assist in coordinating the activities of the forum during the
first year, and would designate a coordinator to work closely with
the forum. 
