The leader of the contingent, Bangladesh Football Federation
Vice-President Bir Bahadur is expected to depart Dhaka Monday.
Bangladesh Olympic Association (BOA) President Muhammad Mustafizur
Rahman and Secretary General Zafar Imam will also leave for Sydney
to join the sports carnival.
</P>
