<TEXT>
<P>
NICOSIA, September 10 (Xinhua) -- Carlos Sainz of Spain looked
set to secure his first victory in more than two years when he
finished the 20th run of the Cyprus rally with a 54-second lead
over Ford teammate Colin McRae on Sunday.
</P>
