title hopes when his car repeatedly misfired on the 18th '
Vavatsinia' run.
</P>
<P>
The Briton, six points behind already-retired Marcus Gronholm
of Finland in the drivers' standings, lost 50 seconds when his car
failed to restart as he attempted to drive to the time control.
</P>
