<HEADLINE> Stam May Miss Champions League </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Stam, who was making his comeback from a hamstring injury, was
forced to come off at half-time in the match, in which Man United
won 3-0.
</P>
<P>
Club manager Alex Ferguson blamed the firm pitch and claims he
